Check Sorted Array:

https://www.codingninjas.com/studio/problems/ninja-and-the-sorted-check_6581957

Solution:

int isSorted(int n, vector<int> a){
  for(int i=0;i<n-1;i++){
    if(a[i]>a[i+1]){
      return 0;
    }
  }
  return 1;
}

